extends layout

block page_name
  - index = true;
  | Sabrina

block content
  div.jumbotron.text-center
    if isConfigured
      h1 You're done
      p Sabrina is configured correctly and running. You can use Omlet to interact
        | with your ThingEngine

      if tutorialContinue
        a.btn.btn-primary(href='/tutorial/2') Continue Tutorial
    else
      h1 Sabrina
      if !assistantAvailable
        if isAdmin
          p You did not configure your ThingEngine to support the assistant.
          p In order to do so, you must have an Omlet account that the assistant
            | will use for himself, and then enable it from here.
            | &#32;
          p
            a(href='/assistant/setup').btn.btn-primary Set up assistant
        else
          p This ThingEngine is not configured to support assistants.
          p You should contact the system administrator to have him enable the
            | assistant feature.
      else
        p Do you want to use Sabrina to interact with ThingEngine?
        p This operation will create a new chat between Sabrina and your configured
          | primary Omlet account. You'll then be able to send text messages in that
          | chat to control your ThingEngine, as your virtual assistant.
        if messagingAvailable
          p
            a(href='/assistant/enable').btn.btn-primary Yes, enable Sabrina
            | &#32;
            a(href='#').btn.btn-default No, thanks
        else
          p But first, you must add a Omlet account!
          p
            a(href='/assistant/omlet').btn.btn-primary Sure, Go ahead
            | &#32;
            a(href='#',data-toggle='collapse',data-target='#omlet-description').btn.btn-default What's Omlet?

          div.collapse.fade#omlet-description
            p Omlet is a chat application (like Whatsapp or Facebook Messenger),
              |  through which you will interact with Sabrina.

            p You can obtain it
              a(href='https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=mobisocial.omlet') here for Android
              |  and
              a(href='https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/omlet/id682042134?ls=1&mt=8') here for iPhone
              | .

            p You must install Omlet in your phone if you wish to use Sabrina, and you
              |  must link it with a Google, Facebook or Baidu account.
